title: Ozzy’s Dungeon
description: Boys and girls battle toe to toe for the opportunity to have their wish granted. Anything your heart desires can be yours if you make it thorugh the obstacle course and into Ozzy’s Dungeon.
alt1: the host pumps up two teams of kids in colorful shirts and gold helmets
alt2: the host holds a giant turkey leg as a kid contestant eats it
alt3: Ozzy’s assistant, a buff blonde woman in warrior garb
alt4: a kid has yellow goop all over his face and goggles
